Why?
I was talking
to Clarke Hayden.

05:17.050 --> 05:20.417
We need to, uh, make cuts
to our payroll.

05:20.450 --> 05:23.908
Carey, we made a commitment
to our employees.
Yes,

05:23.950 --> 05:26.589
and that commitment means
nothing if we go under.

05:26.620 --> 05:27.757
Who was the last person?

05:27.790 --> 05:31.453
Ah. It was Robyn,
wasn't it?

05:31.490 --> 05:34.129
CARY:
We can't let her go.
We'll have no investigator.

05:34.160 --> 05:36.958
CAREY: And how much
have we investigated
in the last two weeks?

05:37.000 --> 05:39.696
Look, it's just for
