05:53.120 --> 05:54.610
Our shop pays Social Security

05:54.650 --> 05:58.416
and payroll tax.
Yes, and you're undocumented.

05:58.450 --> 06:00.714
Look, it's very simple.
Lalo Hierra used

06:00.760 --> 06:03.627
