06:36.660 --> 06:39.527
Step outside.

06:48.240 --> 06:50.731
NATALIE:
Tomas, Elena,

06:50.770 --> 06:52.032
this is one of the lawyers
I was talking to you about.

06:52.070 --> 06:53.731
Alicia Florrick.

06:53.780 --> 06:56.806
