07:13.500 --> 07:15.798
24-hour protection
for his family and himself.

07:15.830 --> 07:17.127
That's already in the visa.
No,

07:17.170 --> 07:19.832
it was promised,
but it's not in the visa.

07:19.870 --> 07:22.703
Also, he wants a promise not to
deport his wife and his girls.

07:22.740 --> 07:23.764
You didn't need to come.

07:23.810 --> 07:25.163
