07:25.210 --> 07:27.701
Good. So put it in the visa,

07:27.740 --> 07:29.674
and we'll be ready for court.

07:29.710 --> 07:33.714
MAN:
Six bodies were found hanging
from a bridge outside the city.

07:33.750 --> 07:36.480
Five more were decapitated.
DOLAN:
And did anyone

07:36.520 --> 07:38.112
take responsibility
for the execution?

07:38.150 --> 07:39.788
There was a bullet
left at the scene,

07:39.820 --> 07:41.708
a single .357
Magnum shell

07:41.760 --> 07:43.557
with the letters
"L.C." painted on it.

07:43.590 --> 07:46.889
DOLAN: "L.C."?
MAN:
Short for "El Culebra."

07:46.930 --> 07:47.692
The Snake.

07:47.730 --> 07:48.628
And is there someone

07:48.660 --> 07:50.764
in the cartel
who goes by that nickname?

07:50.800 --> 07:52.791
Yes. The defendant,

07:52.840 --> 07:55.195
Lalo Hierra.
Uh, thank you,
Agent Thorburn.

07:55.240 --> 07:58.732
Just a... Uh, actually,
nothing further, Your Honor.

07:58.770 --> 08:00.271
We would request
a short recess

08:00.310 --> 08:02.870
to prepare a new name
that we'd like to add

08:02.910 --> 08:04.878
to the witness list.
Granted. We'll break for lunch.

08:04.910 --> 08:06.571
Be back at 2:00.

08:06.620 --> 08:08.872
(whispers indistinctly)

08:08.920 --> 08:10.012
Good.

08:10.050 --> 08:11.039
He's scared.

08:12.920 --> 08:14.911
(jackhammering)

08:16.290 --> 08:18.258
ELI:
Alicia, hi.
How are you?

08:18.290 --> 08:19.928
Good.

08:19.960 --> 08:21.928
What's up here? Hi, Marilyn.

08:21.960 --> 08:24.667
Hi, Alicia. I'm sorry. I had a
bout of nausea but I'm all good.

08:24.700 --> 08:27.737
Um, do you guys mind
if I... if I, uh--

08:30.770 --> 08:31.805
No, not at all.

08:31.840 --> 08:33.979
Welcome,
by the way.

08:34.010 --> 08:36.171
Thanks. So...

08:36.210 --> 08:39.714
this is the new... firm.

08:39.750 --> 08:41.149
It's nice.

08:41.180 --> 08:42.784
We're in the early stages yet.

08:42.820 --> 08:43.809
What do you need?

08:44.820 --> 08:46.959
Mm. Sorry, pumpkin Pop-Tart.

08:46.990 --> 08:48.958
They're the only things
that settle my stomach.

08:48.990 --> 08:49.957
Um, Peter

08:49.990 --> 08:52.083
would like to come by
and congratulate you,

08:52.130 --> 08:54.621
and we were acting as a
sort of advance team.

08:54.660 --> 08:57.026
You want to negotiate
his first visit?

08:57.070 --> 08:59.664
No.
Yes.

08:59.700 --> 09:02.567
There can be no photographs
while he's here.

09:02.610 --> 09:03.759
No contacting the press.

09:03.810 --> 09:05.766
No clients to be informed
of his visit.

09:05.810 --> 09:07.607
No press releases.
Look, if Peter wants

09:07.640 --> 09:09.949
to come here to congratulate
his wife on her new firm,

09:09.980 --> 09:11.345
I'm thrilled.

09:11.380 --> 09:13.746
But there'll be no policing
between us.

09:13.780 --> 09:15.668
No rules, no exemptions.
Just Peter

09:15.720 --> 09:17.608
deciding to drop by.
That's all.

09:17.650 --> 09:19.959
Look, Alicia, the only...

09:23.690 --> 09:25.055
(stutters, groans)

09:25.090 --> 09:26.648
Eli, are you all right?

09:26.700 --> 09:29.157
Y-Yes. I'm-I'm-I'm, uh...

09:29.200 --> 09:30.827
Uh...

09:30.870 --> 09:33.134
No, uh, what, um...

09:33.170 --> 09:35.331
Uh...

09:35.370 --> 09:37.600
Okay.

09:37.640 --> 09:40.677
Uh, I'll be right back.

09:40.710 --> 09:42.598
He ran.

09:42.650 --> 09:43.947
What?

09:43.980 --> 09:45.845
Lalo. Uh, Eduardo Hierra.

09:45.880 --> 09:47.040
He fled back to Mexico.

09:47.080 --> 09:48.718
He... When?

09:48.750 --> 09:50.183
An hour ago. He skipped bail,

09:50.220 --> 09:53.610
and the rumor is he caught
a private plane to Nuevo Laredo.

09:53.660 --> 09:55.013
Tomas doesn't have to testify.

09:55.060 --> 09:56.186
Oh...

09:56.220 --> 09:57.778
(chuckles)

09:57.830 --> 09:59.798
Eli,

09:59.830 --> 10:00.922
are you all right?

10:06.800 --> 10:08.791
(elevator door shuts)

10:28.720 --> 10:30.119
(grunts)
(shouts)

10:33.230 --> 10:35.221
I was wondering
if I'd run into you.

10:35.260 --> 10:38.161
I just didn't think
it would be so literal.

10:38.200 --> 10:39.167
I saw you.

10:39.200 --> 10:41.191
Iwas up...

