Thank you, thank you.

10:56.350 --> 10:58.716
You, too-- you're at
The Outsider Group.

10:58.750 --> 11:02.459
Yes, um, we've been
following each other.

11:02.490 --> 11:04.458
(both chuckle)

11:04.490 --> 11:06.219
Well, um, I better get going.

11:06.260 --> 11:07.454
I have this thing
with my boss.

11:07.500 --> 11:11.129
Yeah, m-me, too, me, too.

11:14.840 --> 11:16.762
Let's have dinner.

11:16.810 --> 11:18.107
I'm-- what?

11:18.140 --> 11:19.107
Tonight.

11:19.140 --> 11:20.835
Let's have dinner.

11:20.880 --> 11:24.805
Um... yeah,
I'd love that.

11:24.850 --> 11:26.408
(phone rings)

11:26.450 --> 11:28.714
Will Gardner.

11:28.750 --> 11:30.741
Oh, hey, Joe,
what a pleasure.

11:30.790 --> 11:33.486
I need you bad now.

11:33.520 --> 11:34.953
I'd like that.

11:34.990 --> 11:37.151
Today?

11:37.190 --> 11:39.385
No, I haven't seen her.

11:39.430 --> 11:40.749
Okay, what's her name?

11:40.800 --> 11:43.428
Diane, who's
Natalie Flores?

11:43.470 --> 11:45.461
She used to work here.
Why?

11:45.500 --> 11:47.468
That was her boss Joe
Pallotta the lobbyist.

11:47.500 --> 11:49.229
He wants to bring all
his legal work here,

11:49.270 --> 11:50.464
but he sent Natalie
to sound us out.

11:50.510 --> 11:51.465
You haven't seen her?

11:51.510 --> 11:52.807
DIANE: No.
WILL: Okay, well,

11:52.840 --> 11:54.034
can you keep an
eye out for her?

11:54.080 --> 11:55.502
She has a case she
needs help with.

11:55.540 --> 11:56.939
We want to give her
all our attention.

11:56.980 --> 11:59.448
Um...

12:00.920 --> 12:02.785
Yes?

12:02.820 --> 12:05.243
It was a good meeting.

12:05.290 --> 12:06.245
She liked me.

12:06.290 --> 12:08.281
What was the case?

12:08.320 --> 12:10.754
Some Mexican
illegal alien thing.

12:10.790 --> 12:13.520
Howard, what did you say to her?

12:13.560 --> 12:16.051
Nothing.

12:16.100 --> 12:18.261
Nothing-- I complimented her.

12:18.300 --> 12:21.098
I said how great
Mexicans are,

12:21.140 --> 12:23.267
how sexy
they are.

12:23.310 --> 12:24.766
Oh, Lord.

12:26.310 --> 12:29.029
She asked for Alicia
Florrick's address.

12:29.080 --> 12:30.399
(sighs)

12:30.450 --> 12:31.542
It's not gone yet.

12:31.580 --> 12:33.810
Call Joe back
and explain.

12:39.250 --> 12:42.413
(ringtone playing)

12:42.460 --> 12:43.586
Hello.

12:43.630 --> 12:46.190
ELENA:
Mrs. Florrick, they took him,
they took Tomas.

12:46.230 --> 12:47.197
What?

12:47.230 --> 12:48.857
Uh, he-hello, Elena?

12:48.900 --> 12:52.461
